The paper focuses on using deep learning to detect DeepFake videos, which involves computer vision (CV) techniques such as face recognition and image processing. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves multimedia (MM) techniques since it deals with videos. The paper also discusses the security and privacy implications of DeepFake videos, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper uses deep learning algorithms, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
